{"tid":216141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食烤肉埋單打交單嘢, 原來係個男人想俾晒錢而個女嘅唔肯","createTime":"2017-04-25T02:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T07:43:32.000Z","uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3db0420b2a61b1efbcf043b0dd99666584bc7819","tid":216141,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到我昨天來了京都與sake公司會面，香港就發生了全城關注的新聞。 今天我甚至見到有網友惡搞一條配音片，將整件事simulate返出嚟，睇到我都笑左（link 我在下面放出來），更加令我覺得我一定要找到事情的真相。經過通宵向同事越洋了解，當然前提係資料不影響警察調查（即係我唔會講肢體碰撞呢部份），同埋一般來講當然我們是保障客人私隱的，但現在事情已經變成全城關注，我相信少少背景情況應該都是合理大家接受到，特別係我留意到報道內容與我了解的事實有少少唔一致，都係講清楚比較好。<br />\n<br />\n客人係7:54pm入座開單的，所以唔係消夜係食晚飯。 終於食咗三個多小時，一共點了3支sake, 3杯啤酒，加埋汽水，淨係飲品已經差不多$1200。 食品點了$700多元，以三個多小時慢慢食計唔算多，我都問清楚同事基本上係食晒冇浪費嘅。 後來買單$2135.10， 男人客用現金俾錢，但係女士都好有禮貌覺得gum貴不如AA啦，男客人好豪氣好好客堅持唔肯，女客人把一張＄500現金俾男手口，個男客居然當場撕爛張銀紙，然後嘅事我就唔方便再講啦（肢體碰撞可能開始發生），後來女客人打電話報警。 但係最後男士都有現金比$2,200, 包括六十幾蚊貼士。 <br />\n<br />\n我聽完都覺得呢對客人其實好可愛，雙方都係性情中人，我真係衷心祝福佢哋繼續做到好朋友，亦都希望冇刑事成份快啲無事。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/poorsimon/photos/a.278479002175491.68360.234282496595142/1412297925460254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpoorsimon%2Fphotos%2Fa.278479002175491.68360.234282496595142%2F1412297925460254&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0b95e2f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/poorsimon/photos/a.278479002175491.68360.234282496595142/1412297925460254</a><br />\n<br />\n又有唔少反女權主義者炒車了."},{"pid":"ad317a23964a661adb67a84d18cd5a48abc00ae2","tid":216141,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa163cb3ea5b49e32aef7d85f042e1a1a035faf","tid":216141,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ca3c5d3deaae7e2ac9ed8711b5c2bf3c0ab6ce","tid":216141,"uid":27537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"好女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c6b89e59a276610f04d99f9f46caa6fd950bc7","tid":216141,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:51:04.000Z","msg":"烤你老母肉，新香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ee761dd75ffe29c15cc22b4efe69cc16f40f98","tid":216141,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a2033f48f226743ad7e0a316cfcb50d49eaa9a","tid":216141,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25d55f1e9ac0e7765d6d6e7eaacbfae263008b3","tid":216141,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbfae495cac2c09f884989a33f45b3dc423bddd","tid":216141,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"冇得怪我地哦"},{"pid":"3331d82b649c7ca1901337bd1fec7027067b89d7","tid":216141,"uid":4150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}